      "content": "他看到行李箱就知道自己也偏离降落点 走不出去了 所以自杀",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "输在没玩过降落伞 我根本没降落点的这个概念 ",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "那怪我 我出题的时候没考虑到你hh",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "老师你人还怪好的嘞",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "那是 你也很厉害了",
