      "role": "User",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "你还有海龟汤吗 再来一轮",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "欢迎光临海龟汤的世界",
